+// SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause
+/*
+ * Copyright (c) 2023 Qualcomm Innovation Center, Inc. All rights reserved.
+ * Copyright (c) 2025 Kirill A. Korinsky <kirill@korins.ky>
